Package org.cvs.application.services

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicationUserService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with application users.
    CandidateService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with candidates.
    PortfolioService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with portfolios.
    QualificationService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with qualifications for specific candidates.
    QualificationTypeService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with qualification types.
    ReferenceService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with references.
    SkillService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with skills.
    WorkExperienceService
    Provides service operations that can be carried out with work experiences.
